00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:30.820
in space you know, not connected to which branch

00:18:30.820 --> 00:18:33.380
of the tree, but eventually, if you keep

00:18:33.380 --> 00:18:37.420
doing this, you'll be able to attach these ancestors

00:18:37.420 --> 00:18:39.800
to the correct branches of the trees.

00:18:39.800 --> 00:18:43.050
So it's really fascinating and exciting for genealogists,

00:18:43.050 --> 00:18:46.970
adoptees, and anyone who has unknown parentage, to

00:18:46.970 --> 00:18:48.820
discover these things that they didn't know about.

